      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOOTIN' SCOOBY (2) comes here off a placing in strong time (19.63) over 340m at this track. In form and looks the one to beat. MAYBE YES (3) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 19.49 beating Payne Cargo. Has definite claims. BLAZING LEO (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (20.43) in a Grade 5 at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings five times from seven attempts. Should play a prominent role. DAM PANAMA (7) is building a nice sequence of placings – hard to fault that form.",
